I only know a few stuff, so other people will fill in the rest.


Vulois Windrazor and Child are at the gateway, studying it.

Brix, Fliq and Ramulus have gone to the moon to gather parts from a 
crashed ship to fix the Ark.


There was a battle at Hell Beast's old ship. I don't know if it's 
over yet.

Iron Raptor is meeting with Arcangel and Feline, and will soon meet 
with Battera. That's all I know. Sorry.
